Togekiss (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0467: Magmortar
Pokémon
#0469: Yanmega →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Togekiss (TCG Pocket).

Togekiss has been featured on 13 different cards since it debuted in the Great Encounters expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Togekiss cards are normally Colorless-type or Psychic-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Togekiss

Togekiss
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
